VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT allowPrivilegeEscalation\s*:\s*true
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:allowPrivilegeEscalation:\s*true && MISSING:# intentional|# required|capabilities\.drop
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects containers with privilege escalation explicitly enabled.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for allowPrivilegeEscalation Not Disabled.
